quran[19{c,v,t}:
38,43,aur hum ne un ko ahal o Ayal aur un ke sath un ke barabar aur bakhshay. ( yeh ) hamari taraf se rehmat aur aqal walon ke liye nasiyaat thi
38,44,aur apne haath mein jharoo lau aur is se maro aur qasam nah torro. be shak hum ne un ko saabit qadam paaya. bohat khoob bande they be shak woh rujoo karne walay they
38,45,aur hamaray bundon ibrahim aur Ishaq aur Yaqoob ko yaad karo jo hathon walay aur aankhon walay they
38,46,hum ne un ko aik ( sift ) khaas ( akhirat ke ) ghar ki yaad se mumtazkiya tha
38,47,aur hamaray nazdeek munhtakhib aur naik logon mein se they
38,48,aur asmayl aur Tasa'a aur zalkifil ko yaad karo. woh sab naik logon mein se they
38,49,yeh nasiyaat hai aur parhaiz garon ke liye to umdah maqam hai
38,50,hamesha rehne ke baagh jin ke darwazay un ke liye khulay hon ge
38,51,un mein takyay lagaye baithy hon ge aur ( khanay peenay ke liye ) bohat se meway aur sharaab mngwate rahen ge
38,52,aur un ke paas neechi nigah rakhnay wali ( aur ) hum Umar ( aurtain ) hon gi
38,53,yeh woh cheeze hain jin ka hisaab ke din ke liye tum se wadakiya jata tha
38,54,yeh hamara rizaq hai jo kabhi khatam nahi hoga
38,55,yeh ( naematain to farmabardaron ke liye hain ) aur sarkashon ke liye bura thikana hai
38,56,( yani ) dozakh. jis mein woh daakhil hon ge aur woh buri aaraam gaah hai
38,57,yeh kholta howa garam pani aur peep ( hai ) ab is ke mazay chakhain
38,58,aur isi terhan ke aur bohat se ( azaab hon ge )
38,59,yeh aik fouj hai jo tumahray sath daakhil hogi. un ko khusi nah ho yeh dozakh mein jaane walay hain
38,60,kahin ge balkay tum hi ko khusi nah ho. tum hi to yeh ( bulaa ) hamaray samnay laaye so ( yeh ) bura thikana hai
38,61,woh kahin ge ae perwar-digaar jo is ko hamaray samnay laya hai is ko dozakh mein dona azaab day
